OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FAsylum hotel closures may  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fshift cost to councils     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Local authorities may have to house    
OL,6, migrants in the very same hotels the   
OL,7, government has announced it will no    
OL,8, longer use, councillors have warned.   
OL,10,FThe government plans to end contracts  
OL,11,Fwith 50 hotels housing asylum seekers  
OL,12,Fby the end of the year.                
OL,14,FOfficial figures show hiring these     
OL,15,Fhotels cost the taxpayer #8m a day.    
OL,17,FSpeaking exclusively to the BBC, the   
OL,18,FLocal Government Association (LGA) said
OL,19,Fthis cost may pass to councils, who are
OL,20,Frequired to house refugees in need.    
